## How to Estimate Synthetics Usage / Pricing with this Dashboard

This dashboard can be used to approximate the cost of using the Elastic Synthetics service given your current monitors. Note that it does not use the more precise metrics used by our actual cloud service to determine actual costs. In some uncommon scenarios costs may differ.

Please note that this dashboard does not distinguish monitors running in private locations from those running on the service. If all of your monitors currently run on the service you can ignore this. If your monitors currently run on private locations you can use this tool to estimate the cost of running those same monitors on the cloud.

Note that pricing data should be determined via https://www.elastic.co/pricing/ , and may vary based on your exchange rate and/or contract terms.
